{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/customizing-nvim-lualine/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yeri's Digital Note"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"11d5dcb9-662b-5b2a-b35a-ab1447191388","excerpt":"Motivation I’m using folke’s lazyvim and the default lualine setup looks like the following.  I want to have a statusline that is similar to that in VS Code.\nIt…","html":"<h2>Motivation</h2>\n<p>I’m using <a href=\"https://www.lazyvim.org/\">folke’s lazyvim</a> and the default lualine setup looks like the following.</p>\n<p><a href=\"\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 4.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAUklEQVQI12OIKpjz39Kv7L+xZ95/54Ds/y6BOWDs6Jv+3947+b+FW9J/bdu4/9aeyf/tvFP+23oBaS8I7eiT/t8zouK/V1T1/7Cc6f9TGrb8BwA1lShzxm8dSQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"default lualine setup\"\n        title=\"default lualine setup\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/a3365fafbc9e7609afe44ece66f8dc0d/fcda8/default-lualine.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/a3365fafbc9e7609afe44ece66f8dc0d/12f09/default-lualine.png 148w,\n/blog/static/a3365fafbc9e7609afe44ece66f8dc0d/e4a3f/default-lualine.png 295w,\n/blog/static/a3365fafbc9e7609afe44ece66f8dc0d/fcda8/default-lualine.png 590w,\n/blog/static/a3365fafbc9e7609afe44ece66f8dc0d/efc66/default-lualine.png 885w,\n/blog/static/a3365fafbc9e7609afe44ece66f8dc0d/d0143/default-lualine.png 1025w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<p>I want to have a statusline that is similar to that in VS Code.\nIt is simple, yet provide useful informations.</p>\n<p><a href=\"vscode-status-bar.png\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 20.27027027027027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vscode status bar\"\n        title=\"vscode status bar\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/4ec4ab411eb5457f88b99f11c51e05bc/fcda8/vscode-status-bar.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/4ec4ab411eb5457f88b99f11c51e05bc/12f09/vscode-status-bar.png 148w,\n/blog/static/4ec4ab411eb5457f88b99f11c51e05bc/e4a3f/vscode-status-bar.png 295w,\n/blog/static/4ec4ab411eb5457f88b99f11c51e05bc/fcda8/vscode-status-bar.png 590w,\n/blog/static/4ec4ab411eb5457f88b99f11c51e05bc/efc66/vscode-status-bar.png 885w,\n/blog/static/4ec4ab411eb5457f88b99f11c51e05bc/c83ae/vscode-status-bar.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/4ec4ab411eb5457f88b99f11c51e05bc/e8d8a/vscode-status-bar.png 2349w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<h2>Configuration options</h2>\n<p>The first step is to reset the options.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"lua\"><pre class=\"language-lua\"><code class=\"language-lua\"><span class=\"token keyword\">local</span> colors <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"tokyonight.colors\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">moon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">local</span> config <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">-- Disable sections and component separators</span>\n    component_separators <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    section_separators <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    theme <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      normal <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bg <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      inactive <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bg <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  sections <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">-- these are to remove the defaults</span>\n    lualine_a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_z <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">-- These will be filled later</span>\n    lualine_c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  inactive_sections <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">-- these are to remove the defaults</span>\n    lualine_a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_z <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    lualine_x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Notice that my setup depends on the <code class=\"language-text\">tokyonight</code> colorscheme, but it can be adjusted accordingly.\nThe Idea is to setup a baseline options for lualine.</p>\n<p>Next, we create a helper function to insert component to the left and right side of the statusline.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"lua\"><pre class=\"language-lua\"><code class=\"language-lua\"><span class=\"token keyword\">local</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">insert_left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>component<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  table<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sections<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>lualine_c<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> component<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">local</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">insert_right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>component<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  table<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sections<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>lualine_x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> component<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">end</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>We can start using the function to add desired component accordingly.</p>\n<p>Here’s the components on the left side.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"lua\"><pre class=\"language-lua\"><code class=\"language-lua\"><span class=\"token function\">insert_left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"branch\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  icon <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  color <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> bg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gui <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bold\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">insert_left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"diff\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  symbols <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> added <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> modified <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> removed <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  diff_color <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    added <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>green <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    modified <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>orange <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    removed <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>red <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  cond <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> conditions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hide_in_width<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">insert_left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"diagnostics\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  sources <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"nvim_diagnostic\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  symbols <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> error <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> warn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> info <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  diagnostics_color <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    color_error <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>red <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    color_warn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>yellow <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    color_info <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cyan <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">insert_left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"%=\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">end</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>And here’s the components on the right side.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"lua\"><pre class=\"language-lua\"><code class=\"language-lua\"><span class=\"token function\">insert_right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"location\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  color <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> fg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> colors<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fg_dark <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  cond <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> conditions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>buffer_not_empty<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">insert_right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"encoding\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">insert_right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"filetype\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Easy enough.</p>\n<p>And here’s the result.</p>\n<p><a href=\"the-result.png\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 4.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAASUlEQVQI12PwDi/47+Ce8t/GI/W/S0jWf3uftP8OQAyiHX3T/lt6pPzXsU/4b+uVCheHYTvv1P9O/ln/nQOy/zsH5vz3iCz7DwAOfyb86LaqcQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"the result\"\n        title=\"the result\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/dd5e854245fefe65564367376eef5245/fcda8/the-result.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/dd5e854245fefe65564367376eef5245/12f09/the-result.png 148w,\n/blog/static/dd5e854245fefe65564367376eef5245/e4a3f/the-result.png 295w,\n/blog/static/dd5e854245fefe65564367376eef5245/fcda8/the-result.png 590w,\n/blog/static/dd5e854245fefe65564367376eef5245/efc66/the-result.png 885w,\n/blog/static/dd5e854245fefe65564367376eef5245/d0143/the-result.png 1025w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<h2>Appendix</h2>\n<p>Most of neovim statusline setup displays the filename on the statusline.\nI intentionally omit the filename because I personally think it is unnecessary.\nBut I do still want to know which file I’m currently working on.</p>\n<p>The lazyvim’s comes with a plugin called <a href=\"https://github.com/akinsho/bufferline.nvim\">bufferline.nvim</a> to display buffers along with its filename.</p>\n<p>Additionally, I also use another plugin called <a href=\"https://github.com/utilyre/barbecue.nvim\">barbeque.nvim</a> to display <em>breadcrumb</em>, inspired by VS Code.</p>\n<p>And here’s the final result.</p>\n<p><a href=\"the-final-result.png\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.27027027027026%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"the final result\"\n        title=\"the final result\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/79643e2ca97191c18228b50fa62fe3c7/fcda8/the-final-result.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/79643e2ca97191c18228b50fa62fe3c7/12f09/the-final-result.png 148w,\n/blog/static/79643e2ca97191c18228b50fa62fe3c7/e4a3f/the-final-result.png 295w,\n/blog/static/79643e2ca97191c18228b50fa62fe3c7/fcda8/the-final-result.png 590w,\n/blog/static/79643e2ca97191c18228b50fa62fe3c7/efc66/the-final-result.png 885w,\n/blog/static/79643e2ca97191c18228b50fa62fe3c7/35a31/the-final-result.png 1028w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<p>Find my full neovim configuration in <a href=\"https://github.com/pirey/nvim\">the repo</a>.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Customizing nvim lualine","date":"December 31, 2023","description":"How I customize nvim-lualine plugin"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/customizing-nvim-lualine/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/concurrent-async-promises/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Concurrent Async Promises"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}